---
layout: base.njk
title: "DeepSeek 教程与文章中心"
description: "浏览所有关于 DeepSeek 的安装、部署、API集成以及日常使用技巧的文章列表。"
# 🌟 核心分页机制注入：10 篇一页
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 10
  alias: posts
  reverse: true # 让最新生成的文章永远排在第一页的最上面
# 🌟 完美的路由过渡：第一页保持 /posts/index.html，后续页面自动变为 /posts/page-2/index.html
permalink: "/posts/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page-{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}index.html"
---

<h1>DeepSeek 核心文章归档</h1>
<p>在这里，您可以找到所有关于 DeepSeek 深度调优与实战的最新内容。</p>

<ul class="post-list" style="margin-top: 20px;">
  {% for post in posts %}
    <li style="padding: 15px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed #eee;">
      <span class="post-meta">发布时间：{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</span>

      <h2 style="font-size: 20px; margin: 5px 0;"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
      <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #555;">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

{% if pagination.pages.length > 1 %}
<nav class="pagination-nav" style="margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; text-align: center;">
  <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: inline-flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
    
    <li>
      {% if pagination.href.previous %}
        <a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}" style="padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;">&laquo; 上一页</a>
      {% else %}
        <span style="padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #eee; color: #ccc; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;">&laquo; 上一页</span>
      {% endif %}
    </li>

    {%- for pageEntry in pagination.pages %}
      {% set pageNumber = loop.index0 %}
      {% set pageHref = pagination.hrefs[pageNumber] %}
      <li>
        {% if page.url == pageHref %}
          <span style="padding: 6px 12px; background: #333; color: #fff; border: 1px solid #333; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;">{{ loop.index }}</span>
        {% else %}
          <a href="{{ pageHref }}" style="padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;">{{ loop.index }}</a>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
    {%- endfor %}

    <li>
      {% if pagination.href.next %}
        <a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}" style="padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;">下一页 &raquo;</a>
      {% else %}
        <span style="padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid #eee; color: #ccc; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;">下一页 &raquo;</span>
      {% endif %}
    </li>

  </ul>
</nav>
{% endif %}

<p style="margin-top: 30px;"><a href="/">&larr; 返回首页</a></p>